findings.title: Rounding error
findings.description: In Solidity, division before multiplication can cause rounding errors.

findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions excludeMultipleAccountsFromFees() and includeToWhiteList() use loops to exclude/whitelist addresses, which can cause an OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long list of addresses.

findings.title: Liquidity adding not in 1 to 1 proportion
findings.description: The liquidity is added not in a 1:1 proportion which may lead to unintended consequences.
